%% Diagram: Diagram 1
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant R as Rider
    participant B as Backend
    participant D as Driver

    R->>B: POST /rides
    Note over B: getPrice + match
    Note over B: H3 candidates (3km)
    Note over B: batch ETA + assign
    B-->>R: match (driver + ETA)
    B-->>D: dispatch (pickup)
